title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings
OB: When calling IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before and after data extraction, the returned labels are different.
EB: IMetaData.getColumnLabel() should return the same labels before and after data extraction, as these labels need to be displayed to the end user.
SR: To reproduce the issue, call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before and after data extraction and compare the results.
